title: NFL ATL: Week 4 Recap
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Week 4 Recap
description:
A room full of heroes, Gregg Rosenthal, Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Chris Wesseling break down all of the NFL Week 4 action. Don’t miss the analysis and key takeaways from each game. Join the conversation on Twitter: @NFL_ATL or #NFLATL.
